## ğŸ”„ ìë™ ì‹¤í–‰ ì˜ˆì‹œ

ğŸ–¥ ë¡œì»¬ì—ì„œ í¬ë¡ (cron) ì„¤ì •

```cron
0 0 * * * /usr/bin/python3 /path/to/main.py
```

â˜ï¸ GitHub Actions ì˜ˆì‹œ

```yaml
on:
  schedule:
    - cron: "0 0 * * *"

jobs:
  index:
    runs-on: ubuntu-latest
    steps:
      - uses: actions/checkout@v3
      - uses: actions/setup-python@v4
        with:
          python-version: "3.11"
      - run: pip install tistory-indexer
      - run: python main.py
```

